#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:168
msgid "Burumardir-Athelorand"
msgstr "Бурумардир-Ателоранд"

# |, no-check-spell
#. [unit]: type=Elvish Scout, id=Elurin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:225
msgid "Elurin"
msgstr "Елурин"

#. [message]: speaker=Elurin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:234
msgid "Who disturbs our forest?"
msgstr "Ко узнемирава шуму?"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:239
msgid ""
"A delegation of the Northern Alliance, seeking the road through to Kal "
"Kartha."
msgstr "Посланство Северњачког савеза, тражимо пут до Кал Карте."

#. [message]: speaker=Elurin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:244
msgid ""
"We allow few outsiders in our forest paths, and no dwarves since the masked "
"ones began to trouble our eastern margins. No axe-bearers shall come near "
"our trees. Return whence you came!"
msgstr ""
"Малобројне туђине пуштамо нашим шумским стазама, а патуљке никако откако они "
"маскирани почеше да море наше источне рубове. Ниједан секироносац неће прићи "
"нашем дрвећу. Назад, одакле сте стигли!"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:249
msgid "No. We have our duty. We must pass."
msgstr "Не можемо. Имамо дужност. Морамо проћи."

#. [message]: speaker=Elurin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:254
msgid "You shall not pass here."
msgstr "Овуда проћи нећете."

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Winter comes on our heels, and your forest straddles the only gap in these "
"mountains. You leave us no choice but to fight you."
msgstr ""
"Зима нам је за петама, а ваша шума захвата једини процеп у овим планинама. "
"Не остављате нам другог избора до сукоба."

#. [message]: speaker=Elurin
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:264
msgid ""
"So be it, then. Yours will not be the first bones to nourish the earth of "
"our forest."
msgstr ""
"Онда је тако. Ваше кости неће бити ни прве ни последње које ће хранити "
"земљиште наше шуме."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:285
msgid "Move both Aiglondur and Angarthing to the eastern signpost"
msgstr "Доведеш ли и Аиглондура и Ангартинга до источног путоказа"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Rally on me, everyone. We have better things to do than brawl with elves."
msgstr "Сви уз мене. Имамо преча посла од надмудривања са вилењацима."

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/09_Forbidden_Forest.cfg:349
msgid "Kal Kartha should be only another day's march east of here."
msgstr "Кал Карта треба да је само још дан хода источно одавде."

#. [scenario]: id=10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:3
msgid "The Siege of Kal Kartha"
msgstr "Опсада Кал Карте"

# |, no-check-spell
#. [unit]: type=Dwarvish Steelclad, id=Dulcatulos
#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Steelclad, id=Dulcatulos
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/11_The_Court_of_Karrag.cfg:103
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:49
msgid "Dulcatulos"
msgstr "Дулкатулос"

# |, no-check-spell
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Tan-Morgh
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:74
msgid "Tan-Morgh"
msgstr "тан Морг"

# |, no-check-spell
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Tan-Garukh
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:121
msgid "Tan-Garukh"
msgstr "тан Гарук"

# |, no-check-spell
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Tan-Wagran
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:154
msgid "Tan-Wagran"
msgstr "тан Вагран"

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:210
msgid "Behold! The West Gate of Kal Kartha!"
msgstr "Гледајте! Западна капија Кал Карте!"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:214
msgid ""
"And under siege, I see. There is a mighty host of orcs between us and that "
"gate."
msgstr ""
"И то под опсадом, видим. Велика сила орковска стоји између нас и те капије."

# well-spelled: Ааа
#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Morgh
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:218
msgid ""
"Ahhh...more stinky-midgets, come to get killed just like these cowards in "
"their den."
msgstr ""
"Ааа... још смрдокепецâ, дођите да страдате као и оне кукавице у својој "
"јазбини."

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:222
msgid "Let us bring our kin that orc's head as a guesting-gift."
msgstr "Понесимо нашим сународницима главу тог орка, као поклон домаћину."

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:241
msgid "Death of West Gate commander"
msgstr "Настрада ли заповедник Западне капије"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:261
msgid "Kal Kartha is taken. Our mission has failed."
msgstr "Кал Карта је заузета. Нашем задатку је крај."

#. [message]: speaker=Dulcatulos
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:275
msgid ""
"Well fought, and our thanks; we were sore pressed. You are our honored "
"guests, and I will show you to the best quarters we have myself. Our lord, "
"the runemaster Karrag, will want to have speech with you on the morrow."
msgstr ""
"Добро извојевано, и хвала вам; тешко смо притиснути. Бићете наши почасни "
"гости, лично ћу вас повести до најбољих одаја што их имамо. Наш господар, "
"рунотворац Караг, желеће да поприча са вама изјутра."

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:280
msgid ""
"A runemaster? There had been none such since Thursagan's day. And for one to "
"lead a holding was unheard-of; they tended towards the solitary life."
msgstr ""
"Рунотворац? Таквог не беше од Турсаганових дана. А да један води здање, "
"нечувено; тежили су усамљеничком животу."

#. [message]: speaker=Dulcatulos
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Aye? Well, you'd know such things better than I, loremaster. Our Karrag "
"toiled for long years to recover the craft lore. He was elevated when our "
"old lord fell in battle against the besieging orcs. Karrag himself was "
"wounded near to death; none thought he would recover. But he leads us today, "
"and his runelore has oft been the only shield between us and the orcs."
msgstr ""
"Да? Па, ви бисте боље од мене знали о томе, наукмајсторе. Наш Караг презао "
"је многе године да поврати наук заната. Унапредисмо га кад је наш стари "
"господар пао у боју против опсадних оркова. Сам Караг је тад скоро на смрт "
"рањен, сви смо мислили да се неће извући. Али нас данас предводи, а његово "
"рунотворство често је било једини бедем између нас и оркова."

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:290
msgid "He has grasped the Hammer of Thursagan, then?"
msgstr "Онда, докопао се Чекића Турсагана?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dulcatulos
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:295
msgid ""
"Aye. Toils over it in a workshop in the underlevels with his personal "
"followers. He has promised all of us that the Hammer's power will smash and "
"scatter all our enemies."
msgstr ""
"Да. Преже над њиме у радионици у исподнивоима, са својим личним "
"следбеницима. Обећао нам је да ће моћ Чекића здробити и расути све наше "
"непријатеље."

#. [message]: speaker=Angarthing
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:300
msgid ""
"That is strange. The Hammer is a tool of crafting and making, not a weapon. "
"What can he mean to do with it?"
msgstr ""
"Чуди ме то. Чекић је алатка знања и умећа, не оружје. Шта је то могао "
"намерачити с њиме?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dulcatulos
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/10_The_Siege_of_Kal_Kartha.cfg:305
msgid ""
"That's for lords and loremasters to worry about, not the likes of me. I must "
"see to my troop's care. Food will be brought to you; rest well, we will "
"speak again."
msgstr ""
"О томе брину господари и наукмајстори, не они попут мене. Сада се морам "
"побринути за своју чету. Храна ће вам бити донесена; потом предахните, па "
"ћемо опет причати."

#. [scenario]: id=11_The_Court_of_Karrag
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/11_The_Court_of_Karrag.cfg:3
msgid "The Court of Karrag"
msgstr "Карагов двор"

